Class MedicalRecords

java.lang.Object
MedicalRecords
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<MedicalRecords>
public class MedicalRecords extends Object implements Comparable<MedicalRecords>
Represents a medical record with various attributes related to a patient. Implements Comparable<MedicalRecords> to enable sorting based on the last name.

The MedicalRecords class encapsulates information such as the patient's last name, first name, patient ID, gender, contact information, medications, reason for visit, and physician.
